      <title>西班牙能源援助终止，通胀率连续第三个月上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/spanish-inflation-accelerates-for-third-month-as-energy-aid-ends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政府取消遏制能源危机的支持措施导致价格持续上涨，西班牙通胀连续第三个月加速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/spanish-inflation-accelerates-for-third-month-as-energy-aid-ends</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
