    <item>
      <title>巴克莱银行认为 IPO 低迷期即将结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/barclays-sees-signs-that-the-ipo-dry-spell-is-coming-to-an-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行 (Barclays Plc) 看到有迹象表明，随着企业高管和投资者对央行降低利率的计划有了更清晰的了解，多年来 IPO 的低迷期正在慢慢结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/barclays-sees-signs-that-the-ipo-dry-spell-is-coming-to-an-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Golden Goose 计划在复苏的欧洲 IPO 市场募资 1 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/sneaker-maker-golden-goose-plans-milan-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利奢侈运动鞋品牌 Golden Goose 计划在米兰首次公开募股 (IPO) 中融资 1 亿欧元（1.08 亿美元），此举将给欧洲股票资本市场不平衡的复苏带来又一次刺激。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/sneaker-maker-golden-goose-plans-milan-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 06:23:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
